strings: <voice_0x01000F53><se_low>The key: I watched my son get his naked heart stolen by a businessman. Should I take him to the royal hunting ground?
<voice_0x01000F54><se_low>The key: You can see everything here. You must tell the truth, please.
<voice_0x01000F55><se_low>The key: ...turned out to be the Heart of Argon, which, with your help, was saved.
<voice_0x01000F56><se_low>The key: Can you tell me that you don't care about size or anything?
<voice_0x01000F57><se_low>The key: Charmels was too old to claim the throne or to be his wife.
<voice_0x01000F58><se_low>The key: This is between me and Shamel. Well done to you bringing him to the right hunting grounds.
<voice_0x01000F59><se_low>The key: The mirror sits on the fourth floor of the Royal Prison and can be used at any time. I asked the staff to pay their respects.
<voice_0x01000F5B><se_low>The key: This is useful when Charles wants to remember his madness.
